org.zamia.instgraph.sim.ref

Class SimData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zamia.instgraph.sim.ref.SimData

  • public class SimData
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores simulation data.

    All signals' values are stored in fAllSignals. Traced signals' values (the whole history) are stored in SignalLog-s (fTracedSignals)

    Author:
    Anton Chepurov
